此地下車站在1937年7月1日，作為跨城線由[[納蘇大道車站_(IND跨城線)|納蘇大道]]延長至[[霍伊特-歇爾美角街車站|霍伊特-歇爾美角街]]啟用<ref name="bde19370701">{{cite news|title=New Crosstown Subway Line Is Opened|url=https://bklyn.newspapers.com/image/52688792/?terms=crosstown%2Bsubway|accessdate=December 24, 2015|publisher=Brooklyn Daily Eagle|date=July 1, 1937|archive-date=2021-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211210175517/https://bklyn.newspapers.com/image/52688792/?terms=crosstown%2Bsubway|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此站設有兩個[[側式月台|側式月台]]和兩條軌道。

